# Stock Predictor (Demo Project)

## Features
- Fetch hourly price data for multiple stocks (yfinance)
- Scrape news headlines (Yahoo Finance) and compute sentiment (VADER/TextBlob)
- Compute technical indicators (pandas_ta)
- Train LSTM model to predict next 12 hours and trend (up/down)
- Streamlit dashboard to visualize actual vs predicted and sample news
- Simple scheduler to auto-update predictions

## Setup (Windows / macOS / Linux)
1. Create and activate virtual environment:
   ```bash
   python -m venv .venv
   # Windows (PowerShell)
   .\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
   # or CMD
   .\.venv\Scripts\activate
   # macOS / Linux
   source .venv/bin/activate
